    <link href="http://houhaosheng.github.io/blog/2015/10/04/vim-notes-1-lowercase-slash-uppercase/"/>
    <updated>2015-10-04T19:58:12+02:00</updated>
    <id>http://houhaosheng.github.io/blog/2015/10/04/vim-notes-1-lowercase-slash-uppercase</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>In order to change the case of the whole document in vi, the following commands can do that trick easily:</p>

<p>in lowercase:</p>

<pre><code>:%s/.*/\L&amp;/ 
</code></pre>

<p>in uppercase:</p>

<pre><code>:%s/.*/\U&amp;/ 
</code></pre>
]]></content>
